        "text_PJxJEe": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>You received The Star because healing is underway. This card appears for those after difficulty, when hope is slowly walking into your life again. <\/h3><h3>You are one of those who must rebuild slowly and intentionally. You may not feel fully restored, but there is something that asks you to take the next step. There is reassurance within you, gentle but consistent.<\/h3><h3>You have this card in your hands because consistency will guide you farther than any sense of urgency ever could. Healing is subtle, but it is happening! Trust it! Trust yourself and be patient. You will work your own miracles. <\/h3><h3>On Love<\/h3><p>You will have many small connections that feel soft and pleasant. To build your own trust over someone however, you must take the risk of being patient and letting yourself be known wholly.<\/p><p>On Health<\/p><p>This is the year for recovery. Be consistent and be less intense about it. You will be fine soon enough. <\/p><h3>On Money \/ Career<\/h3><p>There have been heavy periods of uncertainty that are being curbed by gradual rebuilding. Stability is on the horizon. Take small steps and listen to constructive criticism. <\/p><h3>How to work with this energy <\/h3><h3>Take your time, and go slow. What you want is going to come.  <br\/><br\/>Recommended products<\/h3><ol><li>Sunday Rituals Hair Repair & Growth Oil – Repair & restore<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>Berry Picked Bag Charm (Blueberry) – Quiet hope<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>Artisanal Beaded Bag – Playful Checkered Edition – Fun and hopeful<br\/><br\/><\/li><li>Enamel pin (Lily of the valley) – Meticulous care<\/li><\/ol><p>You can find these in our pop-up booth at Night At Orchard, along the outdoor pathway between Ngee Ann City & Ion Orchard between 26-28 Dec, 3pm onwards <\/p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "marker"
          }
        },
